      • initVertex

        public TemporalVertex initVertex(GradoopId id,
                                 String label,
                                 Properties properties,
                                 GradoopIdSet graphIds,
                                 Long validFrom,
                                 Long validTo)
        Initializes a temporal vertex based on the given parameters. If the valid times are null, default values are used.
        Parameters:
        id - vertex identifier
        label - vertex label
        properties - vertex properties
        graphIds - graphIds, that contain the vertex
        validFrom - begin of the elements validity as unix timestamp [ms] or null
        validTo - end of the elements validity as unix timestamp [ms] or null
        Returns:
        the temporal vertex instance

      • fromNonTemporalVertex

        public TemporalVertex fromNonTemporalVertex(Vertex vertex)
        Helper function to create a TPGM vertex from an EPGM vertex. The id, label and all other information will be inherited.
        Parameters:
        vertex - the EPGM vertex instance
        Returns:
        a TPGM vertex instance with default values at its valid times
